{"tid":1233490,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"話我地就黎輸既入黎集思廣益","createTime":"2019-06-16T19:05:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T10:06:32.000Z","uid":47659,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3c4be6b91b42d0d699c89da8b806acb0dd166cdf","tid":1233490,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:05:21.000Z","msg":"如果政府無回應 仍然拒絕撒回 拒絕問責：<br />\n<br />\n不合作運動其實並未認真組織，大把野可以攪<br />\n<br />\n三罷可以繼續，特別而家sembreak 暑假 有季節性優勢<br />\n<br />\n另外一旦審議爭議性法案（如國歌法)立即去立法會公園野餐<br />\n<br />\n同時間<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣千奇唔可以停</span></span>。雨革係衰無教育同滲透大眾，社會不停分化！我地要爭取更多年齡層去了解同明白大家爭取緊咩野！<br />\n<br />\n但 我地爭取既野要明確！要有共識！要有政制上既進步而唔係消極防守！<br />\n<br />\n不散唔係話你地個人唔散場咁簡單，重點係民氣不可散！！"},{"pid":"50ccf7480458a952a4db6a071a090811a923f42c","tid":1233490,"uid":157522,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:05:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n衝與唔衝，做與唔做<br />\n自己決定，自己承擔<br />\n同為義士，祝你成功<br />\n篤灰割蓆，絕對不做</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"86fcfb4f298d8665ddb5a880c55c9dac688aff67","tid":1233490,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:06:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b3a48ece45a789c3c78bc9be2d764ab8019af2","tid":1233490,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:08:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},